{
  "id": "bilibili-long-video",
  "platform": "bilibili",
  "mode": "long-video",
  "name": "哔哩哔哩 · 长视频",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "name": "标题生成",
      "type": "title",
      "needs": [],
      "promptTemplate": "bilibili/long-video/title.md",
      "humanGate": true,
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "id": "content",
      "name": "视频脚本与简介生成",
      "type": "content",
      "needs": [
        "title"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "bilibili/long-video/content.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "use": "cover",
      "promptTemplate": "bilibili/long-video/cover.md",
      "aspects": [
        "16:9",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "video",
      "name": "分镜与剪映草稿",
      "type": "video",
      "needs": [
        "content"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "bilibili/long-video/storyboard.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-gemini",
      "post": "jianying-draft"
    },
    "review"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "长视频建议 5-15 分钟，开头 30 秒必须讲清「这期讲什么、为什么值得看完」",
    "标题不超过 80 字，信息量优先；封面与标题互补而非重复",
    "封面推荐 1146x717（16:10），大字+人物/主体特写点击率更高",
    "简介区放章节时间轴（00:00 开场…）有利于完播与检索",
    "标签最多 10 个；投稿分区选择要准确，影响推荐池",
    "中段和结尾各做一次轻量三连引导即可，避免反复打断",
    "发布后 1 小时内回复弹幕和评论有助于进入更大流量池"
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "aspect",
      "default": "16:9",
      "aspects": [
        "16:9",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "titleMaxLen",
      "label": "标题字数上限",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "40",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "contentLen",
      "label": "正文/脚本字数",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "1500",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 4000,
      "step": 50
    }
  ]
}
